#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/sort.md:0
msgid "# triton.language.sort"
msgstr "# triton.language.sort"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/sort.md:2
msgid "## 1. 函数概述"
msgstr "## 1. Function Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/sort.md:4
msgid "简介：对输入张量`x`按维度进行升序或者降序的排序。"
msgstr "Introduction: Sorts the input tensor `x` in ascending or descending order along a specified dimension."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/sort.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.sort(x, dim: constexpr | None = None, descending: constexpr = False)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/sort.md:8
msgid "## 2. 规格"
msgstr "## 2. Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/sort.md:10
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/sort.md:12
msgid ""
"| 参数名           | 类型                | 说明                                                             |\n"
"| ------------- | ----------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------- |\n"
"| `x`        | `tensor`          | 张量数据                                                      |\n"
"| `dim`        | `int`          | 排序维度                                                      |\n"
"| `descending`        | `bool`          | 是否降序                                                      |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter Name | Type     | Description                |\n"
"|---------------|----------|----------------------------|\n"
"| `x`           | `tensor` | Tensor data                |\n"
"| `dim`         | `int`    | Sorting dimension          |\n"
"| `descending`  | `bool`   | Whether to sort descending |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/sort.md:14
msgid ""
"返回值：\n"
"`x`：输出张量的shape与输入x的shape相同\n"
msgstr ""
"Return value:  \n"
"`x`: The shape of the output tensor is the same as the shape of the input `x`.\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/sort.md:16
msgid "### 2.2 OP 规格"
msgstr "### 2.2 OP Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/sort.md:18
msgid "#### 2.2.1 DataType 支持"
msgstr "#### 2.2.1 DataType Support"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/sort.md:20
msgid ""
"|        | int8 | int16 | int32 | uint8 | uint16 | uint32 | uint64 | int64 | fp16 | fp32 | fp64 | bf16 | bool |\n"
"| ------ | ---- | ----- | ----- | ----- | ------ | ------ | ------ | ----- | ---- | ---- | ---- | ---- | ---- |\n"
"| GPU    | √    | √     | √      | √     | ×     | ×      | ×      | √     | √    | √    | √    | √    | √    |\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | √     | √      | ×     | ×     | ×     | ×      | ×      | ×     | √    | √    | ×    | √    | ×    |\n"
msgstr ""
"|        | int8 | int16 | int32 | uint8 | uint16 | uint32 | uint64 | int64 | fp16 | fp32 | fp64 | bf16 | bool |\n"
"| ------ | ---- | ----- | ----- | ----- | ------ | ------ | ------ | ----- | ---- | ---- | ---- | ---- | ---- |\n"
"| GPU    | √    | √     | √      | √     | ×     | ×      | ×      | √     | √    | √    | √    | √    | √    |\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | √     | √      | ×     | ×     | ×     | ×      | ×      | ×     | √    | √    | ×    | √    | ×    |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/sort.md:22
msgid ""
"结论：Ascend 相比 GPU 缺失 int32、uint8、int64、float64、bool 支持。\n"
"torch_npu支持uint8。\n"
msgstr "Conclusion: Ascend lacks support for int32, uint8, int64, float64, and bool compared to GPU. torch_npu supports uint8."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/sort.md:24
msgid "#### 2.2.2 Shape 支持"
msgstr "#### 2.2.2 Shape Support"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/sort.md:26
msgid ""
"|        | 支持维度范围          |\n"
"| ------ | --------------- |\n"
"| GPU    | 仅支持 1~5维 tensor |\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | 仅支持 1~5维 tensor |\n"
msgstr ""
"|        | Supported Dimension Range |\n"
"| ------ | ----------------------- |\n"
"| GPU    | Only supports 1~5D tensor |\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | Only supports 1~5D tensor |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/sort.md:28
msgid "结论：在 Shape 方面，GPU 与 Ascend 平台无差异，均支持 1 至 5 维张量。"
msgstr "Conclusion: In terms of Shape, there is no difference between GPU and Ascend platforms, both support 1 to 5 dimensional tensors."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/sort.md:30
msgid "### 2.3 特殊限制说明"
msgstr "### 2.3 Special Restrictions Explanation"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/sort.md:32
msgid "> 相对社区能力缺失且无法实现"
msgstr "Relative community capability deficiency and inability to achieve"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/sort.md:34
msgid "毕升编译器限制，int32、uint8、int64、float64、bool 无法实现。"
msgstr "Due to limitations of the Bisheng compiler, int32, uint8, int64, float64, and bool cannot be implemented."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/sort.md:36
msgid "### 2.4 使用方法"
msgstr "### 2.4 Usage"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/sort.md:38
msgid "以下示例实现了对输入张量 `x` 做排序："
msgstr "The following example demonstrates sorting the input tensor `x`:"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/sort.md:40
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"@triton.jit\n"
"def sort_kernel_2d(X, Z, N: tl.constexpr, M: tl.constexpr, descending: tl.constexpr):\n"
"    pid = tl.program_id(0)\n"
"    offx = tl.arange(0, M)\n"
"    offy = pid * M\n"
"    off2d = offx + offy\n"
"    x = tl.load(X + off2d)\n"
"    x = tl.sort(x, dim=0, descending=descending)\n"
"    tl.store(Z + off2d, x)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

